    "body": "@bidoubiwa, as we don't want CI errors with v3 of algoliasearch, I think this just bumping v4 wasn't enough to be able to remove the ts-expect-error, and they likely need to become ts-ignore instead now. In a next major version we can support TS only for v4, but at the moment we don't really enforce the major version. WDYT? Do you have a solution in mind?",
